long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Universal Keyword Planner box is a keyword acquisition Chrome extension. With this plugin, you can discover much more keywords for SEO purposes.

Are you tired of looking for the best keywords across platforms? All you have to do is install the Universal Keyword Planner box instantly.

*No bloat, no ads, no unnecessary permissions, just a simple way to search for seo keywords.*

To use this automatic data extraction tool, you only need to put your root keyword into the search fields and click the "UK" icon. Then a broad panel will be expanded, on which it displays dozens of long-tail keywords and AI keyword suggestions based on your input. You can copy them or export them to Excel or CSV files (XLS, XLSX, CSV), with no registration or fees required!

It integrates with both official APIs and third party APIs to explore keywords as well as their core metrics such as search volume.


How to use it?
1. Install Universal Keyword Planner box extension onto your Chrome browser
2. Go to any website we support, and start searching
3. You'll notice a "UK" button (the logo of Universal Keyword Planner box) added next to the original search button
4. Click the button, and you will see multiple lists of keywords showing up underneath the search bar.
5. Free to copy or export the keywords you want

Q&A
-Q：Do I need to pay for downloading keywords from Universal Keyword Planner box?
-A：Absolutely no need - you can use any function of this plugin for free.
-Q：What eCom Platforms suppported?
-A：We now support expanded keywords on Aliepress, Amazon, eBay and Etsy.
-Q: Is Any more platform supporting?
-A: We also supported  expanded keywords on Google and Youtube search box
